<p><alert>Example 3.1</alert>: For <m>A = \left\{ 2,\ 4 \right\}</m> and <m>A = \left\{ - 1,\ 3 \right\}</m>, we have</p>
<ol type="a">
<li><p><m>A \times B = \left\{ (2, - 1),(2,3),(4, - 1),(4,3) \right\}</m>, and</p></li>
