<row>
<cell><p><alert>Definition 3.2: (Equality of ordered Pairs)</alert></p>
<p>Two ordered pairs <m>(a,b)</m> and <m>(c,d)</m> are equal if and only if <m>a = c</m> and <m>b = d</m>.</p></cell>
</row>
</tabular>
</table>
<table>
