<li><p>The set of ordered pairs <m>R = \left\{ (8,2),(6, - 3),(5,7),(5, - 3) \right\}</m> is a relation between the sets <m>\left\{ 5,6,8 \right\}</m> and <m>\left\{ 2, - 3,7 \right\}</m>, where <m>\left\{ 5,6,7 \right\}</m> is the domain and <m>\left\{ 2, - 3,7 \right\}</m> is the range.</p></li>
